com.immortallabs.cardboard.game
Class Card

java.lang.Object
  com.immortallabs.cardboard.game.Card
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Card
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

The Card class contains all the necessary information to represent a Cardboard game card. It contains enumerations and "getter" methods for each attribute of the card.

Operations:

  • The Card class represents a card from the game CardBoard.

Version:
1.3, Jan. 21st, 2009
Author:
Michael Brooks, ImmortalLabs CSC309 W'09, Brad Barrows, Rusty Nail CSC308 F'08

- 12/04/08 1.2 More Pseudocoding
- 12/02/08 1.1 Added Version History & Pseudocode
